  "description": "Dataset from the ALBATROSS project conducted by a Consortium led by NOVELTIS in the framework of the ESA Contract No°4000134597/21/I-NB. This dataset contains the sea surface elevation estimated with the ALBATROSS model at 8 tide gauges installed in the Kerguelen Islands. Each tide gauge provides one year of data within the period from 1987 to 2016.",
